<div class="bg-[#f7f8fd]">
  <div class="container">
      <div class="p-5 md:p-10 flex justify-start">
          <img class="h-6" src="/img/icons/previous.png" href="#"alt="">
          <a href="/applications" class="mx-3">Go Back</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white m-10 ml-5 md:m-10">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-tr from-theme1 to-theme2 rounded-full w-14 md:w-20 h-14 md:h-20 relative bottom-5 md:bottom-10 left-10 md:left-20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <img src="/img/icons/add.png" width="50%"  alt="">
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="w-5/6 ">
                  <h1 class=" text-3xl font-bold my-6">Apply Here</h1>
                  <hr class="bg-gradient-to-tr from-theme1 to-theme2 h-1 my-4">
                  <form action="/applications" method="POST">
                        <label for="" class="text-xl my-6">Category</label>
                        <h5 class="text-gray-400 text-sm my-4">Choose Category for the type of application</h3>
             
                        <select id="countries" class="text-white w-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-theme1 to-theme2 hover:bg-lightGray hover:text-black focus:ring-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-white-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-4 py-2.5 text-center inline-flex items-center justify-around dark:bg-white-600 dark:hover:bg-white-700 dark:focus:ring-blue-800">
                          <option class="block py-2 px-4 text-black" value="ML" selected>Medical leave</option>
                          <option class="block py-2 px-4 text-black" value="IA">I-grade application</option>
                          <option class="block py-2 px-4 text-black" value="OA">Other applications</option>
                          <option class="block py-2 px-4 text-black" value="CW">Course Withdrawl</option>
                        </select>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 my-10 ">
                              <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 px-3 mb-6 md:mb-0">
                                  <label class="block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2" for="type">
                                   Type
                                  </label>
                                  <input class="appearance-none block w-full bg-themebackground text-gray-700 border border-blue-200 rounded py-3 px-4 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-blue-500" id="type" type="text" placeholder="Category Type">
                              </div>
                              <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 px-3 mb-6 md:mb-0">
                                  <label class="block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2" for="fromDate">
                                  From Date
                                  </label>
                                   <input id="fromDate" class="appearance-none block w-full bg-themebackground text-gray-700 border border-blue-200 rounded py-3 px-4 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-blue-500" type="date" placeholder="90210">
                              </div>
                              <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 px-3 mb-6 md:mb-0">
                                  <label class="block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2" for="toDate">
                                  To Date
                                  </label>
                                  <input id="toDate" class="appearance-none block w-full bg-themebackground text-gray-700 border border-blue-200 rounded py-3 px-4 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-blue-500"  type="date" placeholder="90210">
                              </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 my-10">
                              <div class="w-full px-3">
                              <label class="block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2"
                               for="subject">
                                  Subject
                              </label>
                              <input class="appearance-none block w-full bg-themebackground text-gray-700 border border-blue-200 rounded py-3 px-4 mb-3 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-blue-500"  
                              name="application[subject]" 
                              id="subject" 
                              type="text" 
                              placeholder="subject">
                              <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs italic">Clearly mention the reason for taking leave</p>
                              </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 mb-6">
                              <div class="w-full px-3">
                              <label class="block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2" for="destination">
                                  Destination
                              </label>
                              <input class="appearance-none block w-full bg-themebackground text-gray-700 border border-purple-200 rounded py-3 px-4 mb-3 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-purple-500" id="destination" type="text" placeholder="Destination">
                              <!-- <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs italic">Clearly mention the reason for taking leave</p> -->
                              </div>
                        </div>
                        <label class="block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2"
                               for="subject">
                                  TO
                        </label>
                        <select name="application[to]" id="to" class="text-white w-1/4 mb-4 bg-gradient-to-tr from-theme1 to-theme2 hover:bg-lightGray hover:text-black focus:ring-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-white-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-4 py-2.5 text-center inline-flex items-center justify-around dark:bg-white-600 dark:hover:bg-white-700 dark:focus:ring-blue-800">
                            <option value="none" selected disabled hidden class="block py-4 px-4 hover:bg-purple-300 hover:text-white" selected disabled hidden>Select an option</option>
                            <% for (let faculty of facultyDetails) { %>
                            <option value="<%= faculty.userId %>" class="block py-4 px-4 hover:bg-purple-300 hover:text-white"><%= faculty.username %></option><%= faculty.username %></option>
                            <% } %>
                           
                        </select>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 mb-6">
                              <div class="w-full px-3">
                              <label class="block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2" 
                              for="description" 
                              name="application[description]">
                                  Body of Application
                              </label>
                              <textarea name="application[description]" 
                              class="appearance-none block w-full bg-themebackground text-gray-700 border border-purple-200 rounded py-3 px-4 mb-3 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-purple-500" 
                              id="description" 
                              cols="30" 
                              rows="10">
                            </textarea>
                              <!-- <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs italic">Clearly mention the reason for taking leave</p> -->
                              </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 mb-6">
                              <div class="w-full px-3">
                                  <button type="button" data-modal-toggle="review-modal" class="bg-gradient-to-tr from-theme1 to-theme2 text-white rounded py-3 px-8 mb-3 w-full leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white border border-purple-200 focus:border-purple-500 focus:text-purple-800">
                                    Send
                                </button>
                              </div>
                              <!-- Main modal -->
                              <div id="review-modal" data-modal-placement="bottom-right" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" class="hidden overflow-y-auto overflow-x-hidden fixed top-0 right-0 left-0 z-50 w-full md:inset-0 h-modal md:h-full justify-center items-center">
                                  <div class="relative p-4 w-3/5 h-full md:h-auto">
                                      <!-- Modal content -->
                                      <div class="relative bg-white rounded-lg shadow dark:bg-themebackground">
                                          <button type="button" class="absolute top-3 right-2.5 text-gray-400 bg-transparent rounded-lg text-sm p-1.5 ml-auto inline-flex items-center dark:hover:bg-purple-800 dark:hover:text-white" data-modal-toggle="review-modal">
                                              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                                              <span class="sr-only">Close modal</span>
                                          </button>
                                          <div class="mt-10">
                                              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg my-4 p-6 ">
                                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between content-center my-4">
                                                    <div class="text-gray-500 text-sm md:text-lg ">From Date : 14 Nov 2022</div>
                                                    <div class="text-gray-500 text-sm md:text-lg ">Too Date : 18 Nov 2022</div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="font-bold text-lg my-4 bg-white" >
                                                    Application for leave
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="text-gray-500 my-4 text-sm md:text-lg">
                                                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.lorem Architecto eos possimus, ullam et impedit quod perferendis enim similique, eius fuga excepturi atque sapiente omnis sint minus nesciunt eaque aliquid nulla. 
                                                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Laborum libero incidunt quod totam debitis itaque deleniti necessitatibus, facilis nisi? Facere illo voluptas atque voluptate cumque repellendus quidem voluptatum impedit nemo.
                                                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Expedita nulla commodi tempora laborum ex illo consequatur ad nemo enim suscipit quo ea, quisquam, veritatis eos error! Sint dolores eius repudiandae.
                                                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Sint quod rerum non iste alias. Veniam error provident consequuntur quas, cupiditate sint enim quia non voluptate distinctio, voluptatibus nobis labore tempore?
                                                </div>
                                                <div>
                                                    <span  class="font-bold">Send To :</span> <span class="p-2 bg-lightGray rounded-lg ml-3">Faculty</span>
                                                </div>
                                                <h1 class="my-4 md:text-xl">Are you sure you want to send this application?</h1>
                                                <div class="text-white my-5">
                                                      <button type="submit" class="px-2 py-1 text-xs lg:px-5 md:text-lg lg:py-2 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-tr from-theme1 to-theme2 hover:bg-white">Yes, Send</button>
                                                      <button type="button" class="px-2 py-1 text-xs lg:px-5 md:text-lg lg:py-2 rounded-xl mx-5 bg-gradient-to-tr from-theme1 to-theme2 hover:bg-white">No, Edit</button>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                  </form>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>

